# Viorra - Cosmetic E-commerce App (React Native CLI)

A minimal cosmetic e-commerce app built using **React Native CLI**.  
It includes **Register**, **Profile**, **Product List**, and **Product Details** screens with UI inspired by the given designs.

---

##  Features

### 1. Register Screen
- User registration with form validation.
- Styled UI matching provided design.

### 2. Profile Screen
- Mock user profile info (name, email, avatar).
- Sections:
  - Address
  - Order History
  - Language
  - Notifications
  - Contact Us
  - Get Help
  - Privacy Policy
  - Terms & Conditions
  - Logout

### 3. Product List Screen
- Fetches product data from [DummyJSON API](https://dummyjson.com/products).
- Search bar to filter products by name.
- Filter button (UI only, optional functionality).
- Grid layout with product image, title, and price.

### 4. Product Details Screen
- Large product image.
- Title, description, and seller info.
- Ratings and reviews (mock data).
- Price with discount display.
- Highlights (dimensions, warranty, shipping).
- ‚ÄúAdd to Bag‚Äù button.

---

## Setup Instructions

1. **Clone the repository**
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/viorra-ecommerce.git
   cd viorra-ecommerce

2.Install dependencies

   npm install
   # or
   yarn install

3.Start Metro bundler
   
   npx react-native start

4.Run the app on Android   

   npx react-native run-android

5.Run the app on iOS (Mac only)   

   npx react-native run-ios

